          <td class="paramname"><code></code></td><td>)</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody></table>
</div><div class="memdoc">
<p>Get the amount of bytes left in the TX data buffer.</p>
<dl class="section return"><dt>Returns</dt><dd>Number of bytes in the transmit buffer still needing to go out </dd></dl>

</div>
</div>
<a class="anchor" id="ga6b1731f98208a52952b57e4505fc6543"></a>
<div class="memitem">
